body: I really hope into the spider-verse doesn’t get soured for me like the spectacular cartoon and the Raimi movies have. Now that mcu spidey is the cool thing to hate, I feel more self conscious for liking it and seeing more mcu fans being harassed. Asshole fans ruin everything.
